title: Ariat Men's Rebar M3 Loose DuraStretch Basic Stackable Straight Leg Jean
description: Extra relaxed through waist and hip, loose through thigh

Nothing measures up to these jeans. The 100 percent ring spun cotton denim is flame resistant and hrc 2 rated. They're dark washed with light hand sanding and tacking to give them a worn in look. Tailored with a boot cut leg opening and low-rise waist. These jeans feature no-rub comfort inseams, extra deep front pockets and anchored belt loops. Atpv 9.5, nfpa 70e, nfpa 2112 rated.
